dialogue.name: natsuki
dialogue.string: "...bleh. I think I’m done for now. I feel really dizzy after that one."

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "That’s ok! Go rest your vocal chords."

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "eheheh... Well, looks like you’re the only one left, Yuri!"

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "Hey, I know you can do it, Yuri. I bet you have one of the nicest singing voices ever!"

dialogue.name: yuri
dialogue.string: "...first having to read my poems aloud to the club... now singing too?"

dialogue.name: yuri
dialogue.string: "This club continues to ask so much out of me."
